===Noun===
{{en-noun|archaeology|archaeologies}}

#The [[scientific]] [[study]] of the [[material]] [[remains]] of the [[past]] and of the [[life]] and [[culture]] of [[ancient]] [[peoples]]. One of the four [[sub]]-[[discipline]]s of [[anthropology]].

